 168:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/list.c ****         *   3) Calling an API function from within a critical section or when
 169:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/list.c ****         *      the scheduler is suspended, or calling an API function that does
 170:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/list.c ****         *      not end in "FromISR" from an interrupt.
 171:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/list.c ****         *   4) Using a queue or semaphore before it has been initialised or
