 173:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/list.c ****         *      before vTaskStartScheduler() has been called?).
 174:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/list.c ****         *   5) If the FreeRTOS port supports interrupt nesting then ensure that
 175:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/list.c ****         *      the priority of the tick interrupt is at or below
 176:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/list.c ****         *      configMAX_SYSCALL_INTERRUPT_PRIORITY.
